<expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu reden und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienstlich und mit fleiss was etc.
                        in bona <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> credencie.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
